{"id": 231436272, "title": "Sonia Gandhi Appointed Chairperson of Congress Parliamentary Party, Kharge's Proposal Approved", "text": "The results of the 2024 Lok Sabha elections have revitalized the Congress Party. A renewed enthusiasm is evident among party leaders and workers. The Congress has been holding continuous meetings. Meanwhile, Sonia Gandhi has been re-elected as the Chairperson of the Congress Parliamentary Party (CPP). On the evening of Saturday, June 8, she was unanimously re-elected during a meeting of the party's MPs from both the Lok Sabha and the Rajya Sabha.Congress President Mallikarjun Kharge proposed Sonia Gandhi's reappointment as the leader of the parliamentary party, which received unanimous approval from all MPs. Earlier, a proposal was passed in the Congress Working Committee (CWC) meeting to nominate Rahul Gandhi as the Leader of the Opposition in the Lok Sabha..Will Rahul Gandhi be the Leader of the Opposition in the Lok Sabha?When asked if Rahul Gandhi is ready to take on the role of Leader of the Opposition in the Lok Sabha, Congress leader K.C. Venugopal said, \"He must take up the position of Leader of the Opposition. After all, the people want him there. The I.N.D.I.A team and Congress members also want him in that role.\".What Happened in the CWC Meeting?Regarding the discussions in the meeting, Veerappa Moily, Former Chief Minister of Karnataka said, \"We need to discuss several things\u2014the way Congress and the I.N.D.I.A team have gained a significant percentage of votes and seats. Of course, we should have won and come to power, and Rahul Gandhi should have become the Prime Minister of this country, but we missed it. Now, Narendra Modi is not as great; in terms of popularity and vote share. I think we are moving forward, and if not today, then tomorrow, Congress will definitely make a comeback under Rahul Gandhi's leadership.\".Lok Sabha Election Results 2024: Sonakshi Sinha Thanks Asansol Voters as Shatrughan Sinha Wins Lok Sabha Seat", "summary": "", "url": "https://www.sinceindependence.com/national/sonia-gandhi-appointed-chairperson-of-congress-parliamentary-party-kharges-proposal-approved", "image": "https://media.assettype.com/sinceindependence/2024-06/ffa2c3e5-f829-4008-8596-69b0f860792e/Political_news.avif?w=1200&h=675&auto=format%2Ccompress&fit=max&enlarge=true", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-08 13:32:19", "author": "Since Independence", "authors": ["Since Independence"], "language": "en", "catgory": "politics", "source_country": "in", "sentiment": 0.146}